{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"iddb29da90-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s248c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"248c"},"text":"§ 248c.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Master account and services database","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"iddb29da91-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s248c/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Definitions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"In this section:","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"iddb29da92-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s248c/a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Access request","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The term “access request” means a request to a Federal reserve bank for access to a reserve bank master account and services, including any written documentation or formal indication that an entity intends to seek access to a reserve bank master account and services.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"iddb29da93-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s248c/a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Official accountholder","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The term “official accountholder” means—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"iddb29da94-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s248c/a/2/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a foreign state, as defined in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s632"},"text":"section 632 of this title","children":[],"tail":";"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"iddb29da95-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s248c/a/2/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a central bank, as defined in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s632"},"text":"section 632 of this title","children":[],"tail":", other than a commercial bank;"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"iddb29da96-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s248c/a/2/C"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"C"},"text":"(C)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a public international organization entitled to enjoy privileges, exemptions, and immunities as an international organization under the International Organizations Immunities Act (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s288"},"text":"22 U.S.C. 288","children":[],"tail":" et seq.); and"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"iddb29da97-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s248c/a/2/D"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"D"},"text":"(D)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" any governmental entity for which the Secretary of the Treasury has directed a Federal reserve bank to receive deposits as fiscal agent of the United States under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s391"},"text":"section 391 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"iddb29da98-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s248c/a/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Reserve bank master account and services","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The term “reserve bank master account and services” means an account in which a Federal reserve bank—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"iddb29da99-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s248c/a/3/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" receives deposits for an entity other than an official accountholder; or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"iddb29da9a-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s248c/a/3/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" provides any service under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s248a/b"},"text":"section 248a(b) of this title","children":[],"tail":" to an entity other than an official accountholder."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"iddb29da9b-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s248c/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Publishing master account and access information","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"iddb29da9c-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s248c/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Online database","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The Board shall create and maintain a public, online, and searchable database that contains—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"iddb29da9d-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s248c/b/1/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a list of every entity that currently has access to a reserve bank master account and services, including the date on which the access was granted to the extent the date is knowable;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"iddb29da9e-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s248c/b/1/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" a list of every entity that submits an access request for a reserve bank master account and services after enactment of this section (or that has submitted an access request that is pending on ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2022-12-23"},"text":"December 23, 2022","children":[],"tail":"), including whether, and the dates on which, a request—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"iddb29da9f-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s248c/b/1/B/i"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"i"},"text":"(i)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" was submitted; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"iddb29daa0-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s248c/b/1/B/ii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"ii"},"text":"(ii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" was approved, rejected, pending, or withdrawn; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"iddb29daa1-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s248c/b/1/C"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"C"},"text":"(C)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" for each list described in subparagraph (A) or (B), the type of entity that holds or submitted an access request for a reserve bank master account and services, including whether such entity is—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"iddb29daa2-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s248c/b/1/C/i"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"i"},"text":"(i)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" an insured depository institution, as defined in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s1813"},"text":"section 1813 of this title","children":[],"tail":";"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"iddb29daa3-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s248c/b/1/C/ii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"ii"},"text":"(ii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" an insured credit union, as defined in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s1752"},"text":"section 1752 of this title","children":[],"tail":"; or"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"iddb29daa4-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s248c/b/1/C/iii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"iii"},"text":"(iii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a depository institution that is not an insured depository institution or an insured credit union.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"iddb29daa5-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s248c/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Updates","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Not less frequently than once every quarter, the Board shall update the database to add any new information required under paragraph (1).","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"iddb29daa6-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s248c/b/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Deadline","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Not later than 180 days after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2022-12-23"},"text":"December 23, 2022","children":[],"tail":", the Board shall publish the database with the information required under paragraph (1)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"iddb29daa7-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1913-12-23/ch6/s11C"},"text":"Dec. 23, 1913, ch. 6, § 11C","children":[],"tail":", as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/263/dE/tLVII/s5708"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–263, div. E, title LVII, § 5708","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2022-12-23"},"text":"Dec. 23, 2022","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/136/3419"},"text":"136 Stat. 3419","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"iddb29daa8-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"iddb29daa9-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"iddb29daaa-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The International Organizations Immunities Act, referred to in subsec. (a)(2)(C), is title I of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1945-12-29/ch652"},"text":"act Dec. 29, 1945, ch. 652","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/59/669"},"text":"59 Stat. 669","children":[],"tail":", which is classified principally to subchapter XVIII (§ 288 et seq.) of chapter 7 of Title 22, Foreign Relations and Intercourse. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s288"},"text":"section 288 of Title 22","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Enactment of this section, referred to in subsec. (b)(1)(B), means the enactment of this section by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/263"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–263","children":[],"tail":", which was approved "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2022-12-23"},"text":"Dec. 23, 2022","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
